citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:00 pm on 15-
NOV-21. The inspector made contact with the licensee via a phone call, and the licensee stated no one was available to
accompany for an inspection.
End Section
